{"word":"G3726 - ὁρκίζω - horkízō - hor-kid'-zo - Adjure","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁρκίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>horkízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hor-kid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Adjure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆணையிடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to force to take an oath, to administer an oath to"},{"paragraph":"2. to adjure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3727 - ὅρκος - hórkos - hor'-kos/3727\">G3727</a>; to <i>put on oath</i>, that is, <i>make swear</i>; by analogy to solemnly <i>enjoin:</i> - adjure, charge."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1844 - ἐξορκίζω - exorkízō - ex-or-kid'-zo/1844\">G1844</a>, <a href=\"#/G1845 - ἐξορκιστής - exorkistḗs - ex-or-kis-tace'/1845\">G1845</a>, <a href=\"#/G1964 - ἐπιορκέω - epiorkéō - ep-ee-or-keh'-o/1964\">G1964</a>, <a href=\"#/G1965 - ἐπίορκος - epíorkos - ep-ee'-or-kos/1965\">G1965</a>, <a href=\"#/G3726 - ὁρκίζω - horkízō - hor-kid'-zo/3726\">G3726</a>, <a href=\"#/G3727 - ὅρκος - hórkos - hor'-kos/3727\">G3727</a>, <a href=\"#/G3728 - ὁρκωμοσία - horkōmosía - hor-ko-mos-ee'ah/3728\">G3728</a>"}]}